le.com/us/album/rotten-to-core-spanish-english/id1066006329|title=Rotten to the Core (Spanish/English Version) - Single by Sofia Carson|publisher=iTunes|date=December 18, 2015|accessdate=}}</ref><br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(performed by [[Sofia Carson]])</span>\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Rotten to the Core\" did not enter the ''Billboard'' Hot 100, but peaked at number 5 on the [[Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles]] chart.<ref>https://www.billboard.com/charts/bubbling-under-hot-100-singles/2015-09-19</ref>|name=}}|| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Ways to Be Wicked (Descendants song)|Ways to Be Wicked]]\"<ref>{{cite web|first=|last=|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/ways-to-be-wicked/id1223549703?i=1223549810|title=Ways to Be Wicked - Single by Dove Cameron, Sofia Carson, Cameron Boyce & Booboo Stewart|work=[[iTunes]]|date=April 14, 2017|accessdate=April 14, 2017}}</ref><br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(performed by Dove Cameron, Sofia Carson, [[Cameron Boyce]] and [[Booboo Stewart]])</span>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2017\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Ways to Be Wicked\" did not enter the ''Billboard'' Hot 100, but peaked at number 1 on the [[Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles]] chart.<ref>https://www.billboard.com/charts/bubbling-under-hot-100-singles/2017-08-12</ref>|name=}}|| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n*RIAA: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&ar=Booboo%20Stewart,%20Dove%20Cameron,%20Sofia%20Carson,%20Cameron%20Boyce&ti=Ways%20to%20Be%20Wicked#search_section|title=American album certifications \u2014 Dove Cameron, Sofia Carson, Cameron Boyce & Booboo Stewart \u2014 Ways to Be Wicked (From \"Descendants 2\")| publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]]|accessdate=December 13, 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Descendants 2''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[What's My Name (Descendants song)|What's My Name]]\"<ref>{{cite web |first=|last= |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/